
Demonstration of Zend_View and Zend_Layout without the full Zend Framework
MVC stack

Author: Lloyd Watkin <lloyd@evilprofessor.co.uk>
Since:  2010-08-10
See:    http://www.evilprofessor.co.uk/269-naked-zend_layâ€¦-and-zend_view/

Notes:
=======

Point a browser at the public folder. Three demonstration modes invlolve passing different 'page' get parameters.

* ?page=index: An index page using standard layout and view file
* ?page=exception: Page returns 500 and uses a 'minimum' layout script
* <Anything else>: Page returns 404 uses standard layout 
